<HTMLAttributesMultiple>
<summary>
The Boolean <strong><c>multiple</c></strong> attribute, if set, means the form control accepts one or more values. Valid for the <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/email">input/email</see> and <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/file">input/file</see> input types and the <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select">select</see>, the manner by which the user opts for multiple values depends on the form control.
</summary>
